# app.R
# Church attendance entry app for two Google Sheets
# - One row per date
# - Multiple mobile devices supported
# - Prevents duplicate rows by locking + upsert-by-date
# - Services, adult classes, and children's classes can be submitted separately
# - Saved values for today are shown beside each input
# - Auto-refreshes saved values every 5 minutes
# - Temporarily refreshes every 60 seconds for 5 minutes after a successful save
# - Includes a simple in-app login screen for authorized users
# - Shows an offline banner and disables saving when the phone loses internet

